      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRUISING NAT (7) jumped from a squeeze box last start but was quickly into stride and led throughout to score (22.28) at this track in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win over 390m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. ASTON CLEESE (5) missed the frame last time at Bendigo but was in the finish the start prior when fourth (24.50) and goes well this course. Can turn it around this time. SAINT RAINE (1) stalked the speed throughout but took over and ran on to score at big odds in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 (22.54) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Leading player again. SICILY (2) has strong claims after a top-three finish from this box last time out.",
